Before anything you must make sure you have gtk 3.0 installed in your computer. If you do not already then run this command: 

sudo apt-get install libgtk-3-dev


In order to run compile the faultsim gui simply run "make gui"

To run faultsim gui just type "./faultsim_gui"

Thats all!



Note: Any configuration files will be automatically saved in the "configs" directory. They are also ran from here.
